{"tid":1696565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美推藍點計劃抗衡一帶一路","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T06:18:33.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c0b94711bdc3fd223339635d50a6ae9f31b0d2","tid":1696565,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/11/06/2296609_cd22c17dc1144dce9bc8718c1db84f0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F11%2F06%2F2296609_cd22c17dc1144dce9bc8718c1db84f0f.jpg&h=9686fa29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國宣布將推出「藍點計劃」(Pale Blue Dot)，抗衡中國的「一帶一路」計劃，建立認證計劃，維持大型基建項目的國際標凖。<br />\n<br />\n「藍點」來自於1990年美國無人太空船在距離地球64億公里處拍攝的地球照片，在照片中，地球是一個小小的藍點。美國商務部長羅斯(Wilbur Ross)早前受訪時表示，如商業公司有興趣進行可持續的基建項目，「藍點」就是能夠安全經營的地方。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》報道，「藍點計劃」是由美國投資機構OPIC在印太商業論壇(Indo-Pacific Business Forum)上宣布，將設立指道委員會，邀請其他國家、私人企業、公民團體參與。<br />\n<br />\n報道分析，「藍點計劃」組織者表示，倡議將成為私人融資的催化劑，但無貸款功能，至於中國「一帶一路」，則有中國國有銀行、企業的鉅資支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2296609/%E7%BE%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%97%8D%E9%BB%9E%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2296609%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=4e041be0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2296609/%E7%BE%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%97%8D%E9%BB%9E%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF</a>"},{"pid":"5f12e4d0a025573f13481deca7741a7d56ae0fea","tid":1696565,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a40a8e7afc6b906d1e46bba05d7